## File Structure

```
SkillsHub/
├── .cursorrules
├── schema.sql                    ← database schema
├── rls-policies.sql              ← security policies
├── package.json
├── .env.local                    ← never commit
├── components.json               ← shadcn/ui config
├── tailwind.config.ts            ← include @tailwindcss/typography
├── app/
│   ├── layout.tsx                ← root with topbar + (auth) sidebar
│   ├── page.tsx                  ← landing → redirects to /dashboard if signed in
│   ├── auth/
│   │   ├── login/page.tsx
│   │   ├── signup/page.tsx
│   │   └── callback/route.ts
│   ├── dashboard/page.tsx        ← my teams + recent MDs
│   ├── teams/
│   │   ├── page.tsx              ← all company teams (browse + request to join)
│   │   └── [teamId]/
│   │       ├── page.tsx          ← team MD feed
│   │       ├── compose/page.tsx  ← MD composer (write/preview tabs)
│   │       └── settings/page.tsx ← team lead controls
│   ├── md/
│   │   └── [mdId]/
│   │       ├── page.tsx          ← MD viewer (GitHub-style)
│   │       └── edit/page.tsx     ← edit existing MD
│   ├── inbox/page.tsx            ← direct shares + (lead) pending approvals
│   └── u/[userId]/page.tsx       ← user profile + Coworker Grade + their MDs
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                       ← shadcn primitives (Button, Tabs, Dialog, ...)
│   ├── MDViewer.tsx              ← react-markdown + DOMPurify (used in viewer & preview)
│   ├── MDComposer.tsx            ← write/preview tabs UI
│   ├── MDCard.tsx                ← feed list item
│   ├── RatingWidget.tsx          ← stars input + average display
│   ├── CoworkerGradeBadge.tsx    ← per-user grade pill
│   ├── TagPill.tsx
│   ├── ShareDialog.tsx           ← direct share / cross-team share request
│   ├── PendingApprovals.tsx      ← lead inbox section
│   └── JoinRequestForm.tsx
├── lib/
│   ├── supabase/
│   │   ├── client.ts             ← browser client
│   │   └── server.ts             ← server client
│   ├── types.ts                  ← TypeScript types matching schema
│   └── utils.ts                  ← cn() helper for shadcn
└── middleware.ts                 ← Supabase auth session refresh
```

